 I understand the troubleshooting process properly. Let me double-check the instructions or documentation for the skill to ensure I'm using it correctly!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"这问题就该走飞书排障，不靠猜。本王先读一下飞书排障手册，再给你下判断。","textSignature":"msg_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7c5a4b2081918dfab204a0b59a93"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QiGi42OTYlQyvj1Wb5WgKo5f|fc_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7c5a57208191836760b8f3291c12","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":90915,"output":120,"cacheRead":2560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93595,"cost":{"input":0.15910125,"output":0.00168,"cacheRead":0.000448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.16122925}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773042770049}}
{"type":"message","id":"075c4d59","parentId":"b07bfc9e","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:52:58.980Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_QiGi42OTYlQyvj1Wb5WgKo5f|fc_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7c5a57208191836760b8f3291c12","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-troubleshoot\ndescription: |\n  飞书插件问题排查工具。包含常见问题 FAQ 和深度诊断命令（/feishu_doctor）。\n\n  常见问题可随时查阅。诊断命令用于排查复杂问题（多次授权仍失败、自动授权无法解决等），\n  会检查账户配置、API 连通性、应用权限、用户授权状态，并生成详细的诊断报告和解决方案。\n\n---\n\n# 飞书插件问题排查\n\n## ❓ 常见问题（FAQ）\n\n### 卡片按钮点击无反应\n\n**现象**：点击卡片按钮后没有任何反应，然后提示报错.\n\n**原因**：应用未开通「消息卡片回传交互」权限。\n\n**解决步骤**：\n\n1. 登录飞书开放平台：https://open.feishu.cn/app\n2. 选择您的应用 → **事件与回调**\n3. 在回调配置中,修改订阅方式为\"长链接\"并添加回调 \"卡片回传交互\"(card.action.trigger)\n4. 创建应用版本 → 提交审核 → 发布\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 诊断命令（深度工具）\n\n**注意**：诊断命令仅用于排查复杂/疑难的**权限相关问题**。常规权限问题会自动触发授权流程，无需手动诊断。\n\n**何时使用诊断**：\n- 多次授权后仍然报错\n- 自动授权流程无法解决的问题\n- 需要查看完整的权限配置状态\n\n**使用方法**：\n\n在飞书聊天会话中直接输入（作为用户消息发送）：\n\n/feishu doctor\n\n诊断命令会检查：\n\n- **📋 诊断摘要**（首先展示）：\n  - 总体状态（✅ 正常 / ⚠️ 警告 / ❌ 失败）\n  - 发现的问题列表和简要描述\n\n- **环境信息**：\n  - 插件版本\n\n- **账号信息**：\n  - 凭证完整性（appId, appSecret 掩码）\n  - 账户启用状态\n  - API 连通性测试\n  - Bot 信息（名称和 openId）\n\n- **应用身份权限**：\n  - 应用已开通的必需权限数量\n  - 缺失的必需权限列表\n  - 一键申请链接（自动带上缺失权限参数）\n\n- **用户身份权限**：\n  - 用户授权状态统计（✓ 有效 / ⟳ 需刷新 / ✗ 已过期）\n  - Token 自动刷新状态（是否包含 offline_access）\n  - 权限对照表（应用已开通 vs 用户已授权，逐项对比）\n  - 应用权限缺失时的申请指引和链接\n  - 用户授权不足时的重新授权操作方法\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773042778975}}
{"type":"message","id":"c19869a6","parentId":"075c4d59","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:53:10.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating deliverability issues**\n\nI think the answer might be yes, but maybe not. It seems that the system isn't necessarily broken; there are likely configuration or delivery issues instead. I can diagnose by using the /feishu doctor in Feishu, but the user is asking here. I might provide current evidence from earlier interactions. I could mention that core messaging works since feishu_im_user_message succeeded, but the cron announce failed, indicating it’s more of a routing issue than a complete plugin failure.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7c5c709c8191b87eab962614e9d2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprnxfDDqc6n7wiWO0S4PWx7gD-zc65JoF7GsclWXXHInHNJRDygqYV06cXfq-nyU_S1yl09kFesx_2BoRJFMm4ciM_pNpT9hCphCxDQMz7HuWDuJ5P6S89w2r-EeW-h-LQU7lpb-HnldBViaERxcZ1D1tA5Ygx6ipNCWhY-jI_D-Ma3O_7bmlOifKxVecyDRfm2YxL1flnMxNQE2KlfopxBjvBlXvnStVZzInrTAd0HUf2JQ8C8FMuT0S85-Zyj38pXPX0eSnDrq0M-N3IVVu6AgQPnudnzvmA2pVpqCERLjC1dMAPBW5pfc2ZQQ8cXWRQB65QdHZdqh1m9fgYqFMdbVgB4b5kZNzF8IqCquAZG-pnUDZzqp8575rEMLEdRemUsj6HqzShdwRdsCYw7A1OU31JhcVn6RiichG1wcdcmUc5bV_p3byhS6c7MGKXpILZQlMkHWCWnHDat7KIvcMR2qZEqD_5_-lagRGcvEOhtqHQrzMBY6TAPSBmJzTJU7MmjWe5SDWJ8p4wjkJUKnW6sS8xfImBi7u1xNs5zoxqUcGB1RpoKyWuSSJeokB3t0lX6Fh1vynq0H3z9cD5O63kJ96HevbiT0irTftXNoy_3j8yN1T-Et4IDLlhGcMxte8wVrRZbXsa_zY-0kpBhkx2ZAWN0XLg8AQn07ZU_5pSsFyePQMmbZv9XwSqWdldFl3_rXKI4dGhwAveHl2DyZ9hUcTDqZCL50XTxv0Uyb1gPJJTI4SnMFoGQQTO8T7PfMLUZEw_SRTr9plD-ooQKwsEhveKl5wf_9lwXzuwDyK42WsGTDxHOZpRLrjikLKaRT7QS85LaxbYdhlk_7aZK9dkpRH0xt8a4omPse8vsmG6EDr0TtYVNGucvwSqQxPTW6HG_K7W4y5KUZiJrXJ5O8JwFi80wyzfmM-dJO1tAKjZwzfXAk-1EssYBj8nDui9o9Cy4AmGMdmAvhisFmKpo_3OXLaaAK8_Skv0JpBLBQ938UD4-IXRb481FwFmzUgVawNqzbxj335f9LcEzwD4rnNd8byCW4bfLSoSVAV6GOOVf5xpfFZRAgXF4P-gOMBnu4e234hVuicNX6h_5mObw9euvE6dbb3I3_3xydIBJLYP6XKbVjSJ9AbCFcRGJO6hWgsiz5KkujGSBJWz2VjeCOis--XYuoUQKICDwGivTkQLSmsf-SWxD5_dvu73Squj26TZbzhD6DgyMH1R8YgjnonPXFbjMxNsdwhOoctYuAYSNkTYabzAEwuq4haFRLA6Sx3-7dW5Slsg7CXO9GJ4Z7hC8zQaSa_butUHCYurdQyyLv3F9JX8y897EjHug7iOOLZcHOn0fjtDbUciYEJmkFP_TuTbw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating deliverability issues**\\n\\nI think the answer might be yes, but maybe not. It seems that the system isn't necessarily broken; there are likely configuration or delivery issues instead. I can diagnose by using the /feishu doctor in Feishu, but the user is asking here. I might provide current evidence from earlier interactions. I could mention that core messaging works since feishu_im_user_message succeeded, but the cron announce failed, indicating it’s more of a routing issue than a complete plugin failure.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"不一定是**整个飞书插件坏了**，更像是**部分链路有问题**。\n\n按本王刚才排到的情况，结论是：\n\n- **飞书用户身份发消息是通的**  \n  我前面用 `feishu_im_user_message` 直接给你发测试消息，已经成功返回了 `message_id` 和 `chat_id`。  \n  这说明：\n  - 飞书 OAuth/用户身份能力没死\n  - 基本 API 通信没死\n  - 插件本体大概率不是“整体坏掉”\n\n- **坏的是另一条链路：cron/announce 投递**\n  之前反复报的是：\n  - `cron announce delivery failed`\n  - `Unknown target \"heartbeat\" for Feishu`\n  \n  这更像是：\n  - 发送目标解析有问题\n  - heartbeat / announce 的路由配置不对\n  - 或 OpenClaw 对 Feishu 的主动投递链路有兼容问题\n\n所以更准确的说法是：\n\n> **不是飞书插件整体坏了，而是“主动通知 / cron announce / heartbeat 发飞书”这条链路有异常。**\n\n### 你可以怎么判断\n如果你在飞书里主动对我说话、我也能正常回你，那说明：\n- **会话收发链路正常**\n- 出问题的是**主动发送**那部分\n\n### 按排障手册，最标准的做法\n去飞书会话里直接发：\n\n`/feishu doctor`\n\n它会检查：\n- 插件版本\n- 账号配置\n- API 连通性\n- 应用权限\n- 用户授权状态\n\n### 本王现在的判断\n- **不是“插件挂了”**\n- **更像“Feishu 主动投递/announce 路由有 bug 或配置问题”**\n\n如果你要，本王下一步可以直接帮你做两件事之一：\n\n1. **继续定位为什么 cron announce 发不到飞书**\n2. **绕过 announce，直接改成稳定可用的用户身份发消息方案**\n\n你一句话，本王继续拆。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7c5f74bc8191937a2faacf48dd96"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":778,"output":552,"cacheRead":93440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94770,"cost":{"input":0.0013615,"output":0.007728,"cacheRead":0.016352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0254415}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773042778980}}
