{"type":"message","id":"a46e000f","parentId":"7873a9ee","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:56:47.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing plugin findings**\n\nI need to summarize my findings about the plugin. It looks like using the feishu_get_user function has succeeded, which suggests that the authorization is okay. So, it seems the plugin isn't fully broken. While there have been historical authorization issues, the current user authentication might be working fine. Let's keep an eye on this to ensure everything runs smoothly moving forward!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7d26126881918dea6d30bc2307a0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprn0oy9Aqp0Md1yEfTRGpa6NGFlEa3vY0BmiGon10jOPGBxQVfbtCHvRP1Et9jOwDqM6QSTESKYf2fzK_J4LtjI2ifHlF0Imy_pWFwXMjOs0MaVgMhN3PlC3UM5A0-bYXlfYdYRzJ3xxlwmLanTGljZeDYt_OtSD24CYFnGqLtRTClmbcu0R00Q40Q2RCIT2od1EGqSFhlwHPNVn10Tpadpxy1bzMZ_7E_tUZo2JwofbWqCqzOA2uy8-9SqaBjYy7bWnsATX2PLsXXMdLxZO51WZYXu-Np4uawgQ33PTerhd-cAYPrqXr0qSMMQJGNGUy444DdFdjwaCm80VTgYTPspUDPKMHD35Ci0_jN6LBT7iV4Eb0yFp6JJDq-18v19DlNmYcvoPkqteaA8Jkkq9PrDwUICKAY466sYZNajx5t9gqHj9JuhWCAGiuIduYuGgENAj-lP_eRO8-uQN6VM3eFi1uADWl5yQ7BV5OlShMLICvJKdoPoLN23AIoF3SnzkrjKDhO0DWTGjshPKbmMFerN2WeVgUwy3e_AOw3jifxMpfZkW1FiTV_m7X1NmNrnBcW2KJVxV7ai1skr9fR7Zykx6F0jrfyEq4-9dh_WzmXnzo_BPG5N4puk3eJQC0DvWCdcZYUVQJAa5dUTM8engOBQWtHI8PdvO_n4Cx6psIzx2oFEa6mG_iJIausmzH3xp5Ez9dYo5AC8rjRXLuEc9qcoH2RbM-yMV5dxHxgqG2m8CGp2qfv1NikPVihc-QyRdB66l5fhaWB4KaPrJ7P7P_p8KI1v3SGv9BNm63FRBEg1Dj5oV4BTWBbhrwz1dmEHEztdg9loPPROxeOWmfUnalx7MNMxRiBD8Ijjf7M0nnNMbyFe351S2lOcxy4-8KDlvU85WdqJsntlg15Npx5-uc0m3YEDEMBAyNV2LJP_lXZNYxHNuKWTKvhuBPVSygJZOqh0uaUpj8W8l61-mPJpJ_cH6nA8pUZ6Kz4pD-XYlEGzn4OfBExCtQD1d3DkVJ_i_UdHrPKs5EarmJ28XSfMpXueHjNUb7O3fjQgvgKDAjSPrydDc=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Summarizing plugin findings**\\n\\nI need to summarize my findings about the plugin. It looks like using the feishu_get_user function has succeeded, which suggests that the authorization is okay. So, it seems the plugin isn't fully broken. While there have been historical authorization issues, the current user authentication might be working fine. Let's keep an eye on this to ensure everything runs smoothly moving forward!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"本王查完了。结论先给你：\n\n## 结论\n**飞书插件不是整体坏掉了。**\n更准确地说是：\n\n- **基础飞书能力是通的**\n- **但“主动推送 / announce / heartbeat / streaming 卡片”这几条链路有明显问题**\n- **历史上还混着权限没开、目标写错、插件重复加载警告这几类问题**\n\n所以不是一句“坏了/没坏”能概括，是**部分功能正常，部分功能故障**。\n\n---\n\n## 本王查到的关键证据\n\n### 1) 当前基础状态：Feishu 本体是 OK 的\n`openclaw doctor` 里直接显示：\n\n- **Feishu: ok**\n\n这说明插件至少：\n- 已加载\n- 基本连接正常\n- 没到“整个插件瘫痪”的程度\n\n---\n\n### 2) 你怀疑的“授权问题”：有过，但不是当前唯一主因\n日志里确实出现过这些：\n\n- `UserAuthRequiredError: need_user_authorization`\n- `AppScopeMissingError: 应用缺少权限 [im:message.send_as_user]`\n- `Access denied ... [cardkit:card:write]`\n\n这说明**历史上确实存在授权/权限不完整**，而且还不止一种：\n\n#### 缺过的权限包括：\n- `im:message.send_as_user`\n- `cardkit:card:write`\n\n这俩分别影响：\n- **用户身份发消息**\n- **卡片/流式消息**\n\n不过注意——  \n**现在用户身份发消息已经能成功**，因为我前面用 `feishu_im_user_message` 给你发测试消息时是成功的。  \n所以至少说明：\n\n- 当前你的**用户授权不是完全坏的**\n- `im:message.send_as_user` 这条链路现在大概率已经通了，或者至少对当前工具调用是通的\n\n---\n\n### 3) 真正反复炸的是：主动投递目标 / announce / heartbeat\n日志里非常明确：\n\n- `Unknown target \"heartbeat\" for Feishu. Hint: <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>`\n- `cron announce delivery failed`\n\n这说明至少有一个核心问题是：\n\n> **不是没授权，而是发送目标/投递目标配置不对。**\n\n也就是说：\n- Heartbeat 想发飞书时，拿了个无效目标 `heartbeat`\n- Cron announce 也没正确落到一个有效 Feishu 目标上\n\n这个问题和“授权”是两回事。  \n就算授权没问题，**目标写错照样发不出去**。\n\n---\n\n### 4) 还有一个持续存在的插件告警：重复 / 覆盖风险\n`openclaw doctor` 和日志里一直有：\n\n- `plugin id mismatch`\n- `duplicate plugin id detected`\n- `plugins.entries.feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden`\n\n这说明飞书相关插件存在**重复/命名覆盖风险**。\n\n这不一定马上导致不可用，但很容易带来：\n- 某些路径走老插件\n- 某些路径走新插件\n- 行为不一致\n- 明明“看起来配了”，结果实际被另一个入口覆盖\n\n你之前说“那个忽略就行”，可以先忽略，  \n但客观讲——**它就是隐患，不是空气。**\n\n---\n\n### 5) 还有网络/环境层面的零星问题\n日志里还出现过：\n\n- `getaddrinfo ENOTFOUND open.feishu.cn`\n- `reply error (final): Error: read ETIMEDOUT`\n\n这说明某些时段还存在：\n- DNS 解析失败\n- 网络超时\n\n这类问题会让你出现一种错觉：\n\n> “同样的配置，怎么有时能发，有时又不行？”\n\n因为它不是纯配置问题，还掺着网络波动。\n\n---\n\n## 所以，授权到底有没有问题？\n### 本王的判断是：\n\n**有过问题，但现在不是唯一瓶颈。**\n\n更细一点说：\n\n### 现在基本没坏的\n- 飞书插件基本加载：**正常**\n- 基础飞书接入：**正常**\n- 用户身份消息发送：**至少当前可用**\n\n### 现在明显有问题的\n- heartbeat 发飞书：**有问题**\n- cron announce 发飞书：**有问题**\n- streaming/card：**历史上明确缺权限**\n- 插件重复 id/覆盖风险：**持续存在**\n- 部分网络请求：**偶发失败**\n\n---\n\n## 最终判断\n### 如果你问：\n**“飞书插件是不是坏掉了？”**\n\n本王的答案是：\n\n> **没有整体坏掉，但主动推送链路是坏的/不稳定的。**\n\n### 如果你问：\n**“有没有授权之类的问题？”**\n\n本王的答案是：\n\n> **有，而且历史上不止一个权限问题；但你现在遇到的核心故障，不只是一句“没授权”这么简单。**\n\n---\n\n## 本王建议的下一步\n最值得优先查的顺序是：\n\n1. **heartbeat / cron announce 的目标路由**\n   - 这是你“收不到飞书主动消息”的最直接原因\n\n2. **cardkit:card:write 权限**\n   - 这会影响 streaming/card 类消息\n\n3. **插件重复加载/覆盖**\n   - 这是系统层面的隐患\n\n4. **网络/DNS 波动**\n   - 这是偶发失败的放大器\n\n---\n\n如果你要，本王下一步可以直接继续做两件事之一：\n\n### A. 继续深挖“为什么主动消息发不到你飞书”\n我去查配置、投递路径、chat_id/open_id 实际落点\n\n### B. 直接给你做一个“稳定发送方案”\n绕开有问题的 announce/heartbeat，改成一个**可控、能落地的飞书主动发送方案**\n\n你选一个，本王继续拆。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0a9d9f33739773480169ae7d28d40c8191a8794c6b026fa587"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":17281,"output":1357,"cacheRead":94976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113614,"cost":{"input":0.03024175,"output":0.018998,"cacheRead":0.016620799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06586054999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773042976097}}
