{"type":"message","id":"7a7fdca9","parentId":"ed941a95","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:20:58.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在不是某个插件坏，是 **OpenClaw CLI / 工具运行时本体裂了**。  \n我刚按你的要求准备直接修，但现在连修复入口都被一起拖死了：\n\n- `web_fetch`：死\n- `web_search`：死\n- `browser`：死\n- `exec`：死\n- `read`：死\n- `openclaw status`：死\n- `gateway update.run`：也死\n\n统一报错都是：\n\n`Cannot find module .../pi-tools.before-tool-call.runtime-*.js`\n\n这说明问题已经不是“我用哪个工具修”，而是：\n\n> **所有工具都依赖同一套坏掉的 OpenClaw 运行时，所以我在会话里没法自救。**\n\n## 结论\n本王已经定位清楚了：\n- 故障点在 **`~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/`**\n- 缺失文件是某个构建产物：  \n  `pi-tools.before-tool-call.runtime-*.js`\n- 当前 OpenClaw 安装不完整 / 更新半截 / 产物损坏\n\n## 你现在要手动执行的最短修复方案\n你在终端里跑下面这组，先重装 OpenClaw：\n\n```bash\nnpm uninstall -g openclaw\nnpm install -g openclaw@latest\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n如果你是用自定义 npm 全局目录（看起来你就是），也可以先确认一下实际安装位置：\n\n```bash\nnpm root -g\nls -la ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/\n```\n\n然后再重装：\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g openclaw@latest --force\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n## 重装后你让我继续做什么\n重装完回来跟本王说一句：\n\n- `好了`\n或\n- 把这两个命令结果贴给我：\n```bash\nopenclaw --version\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n我就继续帮你验证：\n1. 工具链有没有恢复\n2. 能不能读取 `v2026.3.8` release\n3. 飞书链路有没有一起恢复\n\n这次不是本王不修，是**钳子都被你家 OpenClaw 自己吞了**。你先把它装完整，本王再狠狠干它。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0a9d9f33739773480169aec93025988191a4605d9d02b6b8bb"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":190,"output":527,"cacheRead":115200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115917,"cost":{"input":0.0003325,"output":0.007378,"cacheRead":0.020159999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0278705}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773062443331}}
