{"type":"message","id":"8f244f31","parentId":"b7cbb30b","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:30:54.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你刚才**并没有把第 146 行删掉成功**，或者删了但文件整体结构还有别的断点。  \n现在别猜了，直接让我看更大一段。\n\n请运行这条，把 **132-170 行** 全贴给我：\n\n```bash\nnl -ba ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | sed -n '132,170p'\n```\n\n另外，那个：\n\n```bash\n/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/completions/openclaw.zsh:3840: command not found: compdef\n```\n\n先别管，它只是 zsh 补全脚本在非 zsh completion 环境下抽了一下，**不影响我们修主问题**。\n\n### 现在最重要的是\n我需要看到：\n- `tools` 这一段怎么结束的\n- `messages`\n- `commands`\n- 后面还有没有多余的 `}`\n\n你把 132-170 行贴来，本王这次直接给你精确到哪一行删、哪一行补。  \n别自己乱刀了，不然越修越像海鲜市场打架现场。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0a9d9f33739773480169aecb86df208191904f31e8689fee5c"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1825,"output":252,"cacheRead":120064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122141,"cost":{"input":0.00319375,"output":0.003528,"cacheRead":0.0210112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02773295}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773063038267}}
