{"type":"message","id":"7c112eff","parentId":"034ed4e0","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:36:45.865Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-09 21:36 GMT+8] Last login: Mon Mar 9 21:32:31 on ttys006\n/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/completions/openclaw.zsh:3840: command not found: compdef\nsuchuanlei@Mac ~ % openclaw status openclaw doctor \n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.8 (3caab92)\n The only open-source project where the mascot could eat the competition.\n\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_get_user: Registered feishu_get_user tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_search_user: Registered feishu_search_user tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_chat_members: Registered feishu_chat_members tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat, feishu_chat_members\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_im_user_message: Registered feishu_im_user_message tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_im_user_fetch_resource: Registered feishu_im_user_fetch_resource tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_calendar_calendar: Registered feishu_calendar_calendar tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_calendar_event: Registered feishu_calendar_event tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_calendar_event_attendee: Registered feishu_calendar_event_attendee tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_calendar_freebusy: Registered feishu_calendar_freebusy tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_task_task: Registered feishu_task_task tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_task_tasklist: Registered feishu_task_tasklist tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_task_comment: Registered feishu_task_comment tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_task_subtask: Registered feishu_task_subtask tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_bitable_app: Registered feishu_bitable_app tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_bitable_app_table: Registered feishu_bitable_app_table tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_bitable_app_table_record: Registered feishu_bitable_app_table_record tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_bitable_app_table_field: Registered feishu_bitable_app_table_field tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_bitable_app_table_view: Registered feishu_bitable_app_table_view tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_search_doc_wiki: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_search: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_drive_file: Registered feishu_drive_file tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_doc_comments: Registered feishu_doc_comments tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_doc_media: Registered feishu_doc_media tool (insert, download)\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_wiki_space: Registered feishu_wiki_space tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_wiki_space_node: Registered feishu_wiki_space_node tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_sheet: Registered feishu_sheet tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_im_bot_image: Registered feishu_im_bot_image tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\n21:36:32 [plugins] ✅ Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, mail, search, drive, wiki, sheets, okr, im)\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\n21:36:32 [plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\n│\n21:36:35 [memory] fts unavailable: no such module: fts5\n◇ \n│\n◇ \nOpenClaw status\n\nOverview\n┌───────────